      <odd id="aspace_fd2012b3b95e7b2b40bb6d67899e2985">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 14-A (YRG 14-A), Records of governing bodies and committees of the Yale Faculty of Arts and Sciences.</p>
      </odd>
